Original Author: Maciej Gębala
Modified by Agnieszka Głuszkiewicz for educational purposes.

Files:

Makefile
board.h         // game rules and board handling
game_server.c   // game server
game_client.c   // game client for human players
minimax_bot.c // game bot using the Minimax algorithm with Alpha-Beta pruning

Compiler: gcc version 13.3.0
Library: gsl 2.7 (my_minimax_bot - random number generator)


Server Execution:

./game_server <ip_address> <port_number>

Human Client Execution:

./game_client <ip_address> <port_number> <player_number> <nickname>

Minimax Bot Execution:

./minimax_bot <ip_address> <port_number> <player_number> <nickname> <search_depth>


player_number: 1 for X or 2 for O.
nickname: player identifier (name) (up to 9 characters)
search_depth: depth for the Minimax algorithm's search (integer from 1 to 10)